### App
https://github.com/material-components/material-components-flutter-experimental/tree/master/advanced

### Steps to recreate
1. Run app
1. Click on 'Crane' button
1. Open inspector and enter selection mode
1. See error #⁠1
1. Close selction mode
1. See error #⁠2

comment_data.body: Must have been in some weird state. I downgraded to 1.2.1 to use the inspector (it worked.) And then upgraded back to master 1.2.3-pre.29. Issue not reproduced anymore.
@jacob314 This looks like an inspector issue.
Am I in the wrong repo?
I think you're in the right place.

Thanks for the great repro steps! I'll take a look at what is happening.
Technically this is the package:flutter bug but I'm the right person to fix it so it doesn't matter much.

Merging reports of this issue into.
https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/25707
